          <div class="item-1"> <img src="<%=data1.Homeurl%>" class="card-img-top" alt="..." /></div>
          <div class="item-2"> <img src="<%=data1.Homeurl%>" class="card-img-top" alt="..." /></div>
          <div class="item-3"> <img src="<%=data1.Homeurl%>" class="card-img-top" alt="..." /></div>
          <div class="item-4"> <img src="<%=data1.Homeurl%>" class="card-img-top" alt="..." /></div>
          <div class="item-5"> <img src="<%=data1.Homeurl%>" class="card-img-top" alt="..." /></div>
      </div>
       <!-- imagegrid section ends here -->
       <!-- about section starts here -->
      <div class="about">
        <span><h2><i class="fa-solid fa-house-user"></i></i> About Home</h2></span>
        <p>Mary Place retains all the proportions of the original artisanal cottage, complete with the chimneys and fireplaces; pretty sash windows and tiny staircases that snake right up into the rooftop third bedroom. The style of the cottage is unique, decorated by Collette Dinnigan with her signature mix of fine country antiques, beautiful bed linen, towels, and eclectic paintings. The tiny private courtyard trimmed with evergreen shrubs and annual flowers - opens out.</p>
        <span><h5><i class="fa-solid fa-building-wheat"></i> Home Type:</h5></span>
       <p> <%=data1.PropertyType%></p> 
        <span><h5><i class="fa-solid fa-restroom"></i> Room Type:</h5></span>
        <p>Home/Appartments</p>
        <span><h5><i class="fa-solid fa-moon"></i> Minimum Nights:</h5></span>
        <p>3</p>
        <span><h5><i class="fa-sharp fa-solid fa-street-view"></i> Overview:</h5></span>
        <p> Feel like royalty with every visit to our elegant hotel suites.</p>
        <span><h5><i class="fa-solid fa-file"></i> Policy</h5></span>
        <p>Moderate</p>
      </div>
       <!-- about section ends here -->
         <!-- review section starts here -->
      <div class="review">
        <div class="review-left">
          <div class="review_logo">
            <img src="https://a0.muscache.com/im/pictures/f4a1e0fb-bd06-4f11-91e3-8d3979d3431a.jpg" alt="airbnb logo" />
          </div>
         
          <h4>What this place offers</h4>
          <div class="offers">
            <span><p><i class="fa-solid fa-eye"></i>   Eye</span></p>      
            <span><p><i class="fa-solid fa-kitchen-set"></i>  Essentials</span> </p>
            <span><p><i class="fa-solid fa-briefcase"></i>   Air conditioning</span></p>
            <span><p><i class="fa-sharp fa-solid fa-building"></i>   Kitchen</span> </p>
            <span><p><i class="fa-solid fa-wifi"></i>   Wifi </span></p>
            <span><p><i class="fa-solid fa-umbrella-beach"></i>  Free street parking</span> </p>
            <span><p><i class="fa-sharp fa-solid fa-dog"></i>  Dogs<span></p>
            
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="review-right">
          <div class="reserved">
             <!-- booking form section starts here -->
            <form name="myForm"  action="">
            <h3>Book Your Home.</h3>
            <p>Total price :<b>‚Çπ<%=data1.Price%></b></p>
             
          <div class="form-group">
            <input class="form-control" type="date" name="fname" required>
            <span class="form-label">Check In</span>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <input class="form-control" type="date" required>
          <span class="form-label">Check out</span>
      </div>
      <div class="form-group">
        <select class="form-control" required>
            <option value="" selected hidden>no of rooms</option>
            <option>1</option>
            <option>2</option>
            <option>3</option>
        </select>
        <span class="select-arrow"></span>
        <span class="form-label">Rooms</span>
    </div>
    <div class="form-group">
      <select class="form-control" required>
          <option value="" selected hidden>no of adults</option>
          <option>1</option>
          <option>2</option>
          <option>3</option>
      </select>
      <span class="select-arrow"></span>
      <span class="form-label">Adults</span>
    </div>
    <div class="form-btn">
      <button class="submit-btn" type="submit" id="form-submit" onclick="validateForm()">Book Now</button>
    </div>
    </div>
        </div>
      </div>
